{"tid":2311123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「千萬求一路」疑爛尾 百萬酬金無影 政協兼發起人：我唔會走數","createTime":"2020-12-03T23:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T01:05:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3f4a4ebb85cd36a3aec23d433a0b3db843c991","tid":2311123,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:06:54.000Z","msg":"哈爾濱市政協莊紫祥去年9月發起「1000萬求一路」比賽，揚言豪擲1,000萬元鼓勵市民參與獻策，以解決因修訂《逃犯條例》造成的社會困局，成功吸引逾15萬市民參與。但《蘋果》發現比賽已結束逾半年，但逾千名得獎評選員之中有不少人仍被拖欠酬金，每人遭拖欠數百元至18萬元不等，料欠款總金額或數以百萬元計，質疑比賽爛尾。事主稱就連主辦者「尋路人有限公司」辦公室亦人去樓空，擔心難以追討，亦關注得獎評選員曾呈交的身份證及銀行賬戶等私隱資料會否獲得保障。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201201/PPZFGGB47RCQRJACECO73WVVX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201201%2FPPZFGGB47RCQRJACECO73WVVX4%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=e2f1d5dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201201%2FPPZFGGB47RCQRJACECO73WVVX4%2F&h=36581877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201201/PPZFGGB47RCQRJACECO73WVVX4/</a>"},{"pid":"056b846177f451f9133a448a6f464fe570ce4c02","tid":2311123,"uid":194588,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:10:33.000Z","msg":"搞撚笑<br />\n真係祖國縮影<br />\n搞PR都要造假縱要比人踢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d90951d08d0cbf42da944203e07a1d49288f70","tid":2311123,"uid":264771,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:12:59.000Z","msg":"係中國最開心既係可以當班人馬騮咁玩之後唔洗負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5d2f9c74ced91c78f098124a5327e464c02adb","tid":2311123,"uid":242921,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:14:28.000Z","msg":"15萬人參加，世界蠢人真多。"},{"pid":"bb285d0383988a4bccc32ed8d0f72520adc1b0ac","tid":2311123,"uid":282347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:19:4